data.description: Living the life of LUXURY! Custom built by Vintage Estate Homes, located in the prestigious community of Vintage Oaks. More than an acre lot w/many mature oak trees. The family room boasts a gas burning limestone fireplace w/detailed stonework and opens up to a 22 x 20 covered patio w/12 foot pocket sliding doors to enjoy the summer breeze and entertain family and friends! The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream equipped w/top-of-the-line appliances, Bertazonni double convection ovens, vent, and dishwasher, Thermidor 6 burner gas range w/griddle, pot-filler above range, upgraded granite countertops and an abundance of Michael Edwards custom built cabinets. Yamaha audio/video receiver w/Sonance built in speakers, Rockwood custom 4" wood shutters throughout w/invisible tilt, barn doors entering game room and theatre room, 8' doors throughout w/14' ceilings and powder room w/exterior door for pool access. Blaze outdoor kitchen w/grill, sink, refrigerator, and Primo smoker. 2 Tankless water heaters. Life-source whole house water filter system. Coated garage floor w/lifetime warranty. Walk up attic access to floored storage. 6'-foot wrought iron fence throughout backyard and custom Keith Zars gunite pool w/heated spa. Vintage Oaks resort-style amenities are second to none! Lazy River Pool, Tennis Courts, Soccer Field, Volleyball Court, 7,800 SqFt Fitness Club, Tuscan-Style Clubhouse, 5 miles of Trails through rolling hills, Olympic-sized Pool, Children's Playground and so much more! Just minutes away from the heart of New Braunfels, exceptional schools, parks, rivers, and shopping. There are too many amenities to list...MUST see to appreciate!!
